{"blogid": "126742302", "writerAge": "码龄4年", "writerBlogNum": "239", "writerCollect": "818", "writerComment": "115", "writerFan": "218", "writerGrade": "5级", "writerIntegral": "3610", "writerName": "beidou111", "writerProfileAdress": "writer_image\\profile_126742302.jpg", "writerRankTotal": "5273", "writerRankWeekly": "8281", "writerThumb": "223", "writerVisitNum": "204056", "blog_read_count": "13", "blog_time": "于 2022-09-07 11:40:26 发布", "blog_title": "win10+VSCode+cmake 安装glut, cmake链接静态库", "content": "<div class=\"article_content clearfix\" id=\"article_content\">\n<link href=\"style.css\" rel=\"stylesheet\"/>\n<div class=\"markdown_views prism-atom-one-light\" id=\"content_views\">\n<svg style=\"display: none;\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\n<path d=\"M5,0 0,2.5 5,5z\" id=\"raphael-marker-block\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);\"></path>\n</svg>\n<p>配置：win10+VSCode+cmake插件</p>\n<h1><a id=\"glut_2\"></a>下载glut</h1>\n<p><a href=\"https://user.xmission.com/~nate/glut.html\">https://user.xmission.com/~nate/glut.html</a></p>\n<p>只要拷贝这两个文件即可<br/> <img alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" src=\"image\\8567ace18ed241f4870f6655ae4ea7f8.png\"/></p>\n<h1><a id=\"_8\"></a>目录结构</h1>\n<p><img alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" src=\"image\\6aba1009c4df46e39ed354a30bcb55c2.png\"/></p>\n<h1><a id=\"_CMakeListstxt_12\"></a>项目设置 CMakeLists.txt</h1>\n<p>CMakeLists.txt文件</p>\n<pre><code class=\"prism language-cpp\"><span class=\"token function\">cmake_minimum_required</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>VERSION <span class=\"token number\">3.20</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token function\">project</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>opengl<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n\n<span class=\"token function\">include_directories</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>glut<span class=\"token operator\">/</span>include<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n\n<span class=\"token function\">link_directories</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>glut<span class=\"token operator\">/</span>lib<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n\n<span class=\"token function\">add_executable</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>main main<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>cpp<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n\n<span class=\"token function\">target_link_directories</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>main PUBLIC glut32<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>lib<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n</code></pre>\n<p>说明<br/> cmake_minimum_required 声明cmake最小版本<br/> project(opengl) 设置项目名<br/> include_directories(glut/include)添加include路径<br/> link_directories(glut/lib) 添加库文件路径<br/> add_executable(main main.cpp) 编译目标: 生成一个main.exe<br/> target_link_directories(main PUBLIC glut32.lib) 把glut32.lib链接到main.exe</p>\n<h1><a id=\"_36\"></a>注意事项</h1>\n<p>注意：windows下面的静态文件叫.lib，动态库叫.dll<br/> linux下面的静态库叫.a，动态库叫.so</p>\n<p>请注意分辨，不要下载错了版本<br/> 不然会出现如下错误</p>\n<pre><code class=\"prism language-cpp\">连接静态库 LINK <span class=\"token operator\">:</span> fatal error LNK1104<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> 无法打开文件“glut32<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>a<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>lib”\n</code></pre>\n<p>你会惊诧于为什么自己加了个.lib后缀？实际上是因为.a版本没法用在windows</p>\n</div>\n<link href=\"https://csdnimg.cn/release/blogv2/dist/mdeditor/css/editerView/markdown_views-22a2fefd3b.css\" rel=\"stylesheet\"/>\n<link href=\"https://csdnimg.cn/release/blogv2/dist/mdeditor/css/style-4f8fbf9108.css\" rel=\"stylesheet\"/>\n</div>"}